sql_query.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."account_id" = $1

SELECT coalesce(nullif(accounts.shared_inbox_url, ''), accounts.inbox_url) AS preferred_inbox_url FROM "accounts" INNER JOIN "follows" ON "accounts"."id" = "follows"."account_id" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND "accounts"."protocol" = $2 GROUP BY "preferred_inbox_url"
SELECT coalesce(nullif(accounts.shared_inbox_url, ''), accounts.inbox_url) AS preferred_inbox_url FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."protocol" = $1 GROUP BY "preferred_inbox_url"
